title: Companies on the Norwegian insurance market 2011 to 2015
summary: The given chart is of multi-line type with 2 lines namely Domestic market, and Total market. The y axis represents Number of companies and the x axis represents Year.
Overall Domestic market, and Total market are roughly constant,  throughout the Year
The lines ordered according to average values of Number of companies in descending order is: 1. Total market, and lastly, 2. Domestic market.

Throughout the period, Total market generally had the highest Number of companies relative to others with an average of 118.4, and it reached its maximum at 2013, 2014, and 2015 with a value of 119.0.
The botommost line, Domestic market,  has a mean of 118.4, and peaked at 2013, 2014, and 2015.
